data.description: Better than a new build with no wait time! This gorgeous 2021 Pulte home is ready for its new owners. It features over 2,700 sq feet of living space and is normally a 3 bedroom home with a loft. However, this home was built with a fourth bedroom and full bathroom to act as a mother in law suite. The large open concept on the first floor flows beautifully from the kitchen to the living room with a ''planning area'' that has been converted to a mini bar. Rounding out the first floor, there is space for an office or playroom with French doors to make it what you want. A full basement awaits downstairs to be finished with endless possibilities. This home has everything you could ask for in a move in ready property! Come check it out.
